-- Britain’s Dujardin Wins Equestrianism Gold Medal in Dressage
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-08-09T15:12:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-09/britain-s-dujardin-wins-equestrianism-gold-medal-in-dressage.html
Britain’s  Charlotte  Dujardin
won the Olympic gold medal in individual freestyle equestrian
dressage.  Adelinde Cornelissen of the Netherlands came second and
Laura Bechtolsheimer of Britain was third at Greenwich Park in
southeast London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  